Battera::

She looked at CryberShark. Her face showed her puzzlement. "So you 
got damaged and made a new body for yourself?" 

She wondered just how long she had been away from him.

"And your now connected to Magmatron? How?" She took a step closer to 
him, and looked into his eye. She could see that it was CyberShark 
inside there. She relaxed and smiled. "And you like this change?"
She smiled and leaned forward. She kissed him. She knew that if it 
was him, she'd still feel the fire in his kiss.
